// Copy this file to Signing.local.xcconfig and fill in your Apple Developer
// team ID. The real Signing.local.xcconfig is gitignored.
//
// Find your team ID at https://developer.apple.com/account under
// "Membership details" or by running in Terminal:
//   security find-identity -v -p codesigning
// (team ID appears in parens at the end of each identity name).
//
// If you're just building locally without a paid Apple Developer account,
// leave this empty. The build will use ad-hoc signing or fail, depending
// on your Xcode settings.

LOCAL_DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID_HERE
